<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">调整分配法，在计算时，遇到不能直接运用分配率的题目，但含有使用分配率的因数，如能做适当的调整，就可使用分配率，进行速算。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">a×b×c×d×e=(a×d)×b×c×e</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算。</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">19×12×25=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">19×12×25</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=19×(12×25)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=19×300</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=5700</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>